desc: Compilation of interviews with famous celebrities discussing their latest projects and personal lives.

sttData.content: Award-winning actress, Scarlett Johansson, sits down with us to discuss her latest film, "The Souvenir", and talks about her experience playing a complex character.
Music sensation, Billie Eilish, shares her thoughts on her breakthrough album, "When We All Fall Asleep, Where Do We Go?," and reveals her creative process.
Acclaimed actor, Tom Hanks, talks about his role in the drama series, "Grey's Anatomy", and shares insights into his long-lasting career.
Comedian, Kevin Hart, shares his journey from struggling comedian to a household name, and talks about the challenges he's faced along the way.
Legendary actress, Meryl Streep, shares her experiences working with iconic directors, reveals her favorite roles, and talks about the importance of staying creative throughout her career.

stt.sttSummary: Celebrity interviews discussing their latest projects and personal lives. Interviewees include Scarlett Johansson, Billie Eilish, Tom Hanks, Kevin Hart, and Meryl Streep.
